Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:41.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\yshad3}拉开帷幕的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.57,0:01:46.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\yshad3}让人感到心潮澎湃
