Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:05.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\yshad3}如同星辰般的海浪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:09.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\yshad3}美丽永恒的光辉
